This is a FY 2026 New Start funded with $0.600 million, no increase/decrease. Transition strategy: With the Pacific Autonomous
Aircraft Capability - Light Intra-Theater Logistic (PAAC-LITL) effort getting fully underway under the auspices of Pacific Air Forces
Operations Directorate (PACAF A3) and the Logistics, Engineering, and Force Protection Directorate (PACAF A4) in FY25, the
natural transition target is PACAF. Transition path likely found in treating RALPH as a simple tool that can be secured by users as
a General Services Administration (GSA) commodity.
