supports the PEO Soldier's requirement for Small Unit Resupply (SUR) and SUR Decision Dominance, documented as a need
within Project Polaris, Close Combat Integration Enterprise Modernization Plan 2024.
Title: Synthetic Data Generation Engine                                                                                                           -       0.000          0.362
