Funding increases in FY 2026 due to furthered efforts in architecture development to ensure the technical integrity of the system
of systems integration cross-cutting air, space, maritime, land, and homeland defense domains to integrate the DAF BATTLE
NETWORK. Furthermore, integrated digital environment (IDE) efforts continue to scale across all 5 MITs in FY26 to provide a

