 2030, and Multi-Domain Command and Control [MDC2]), or correction of field deficiencies.

 Tanker Recapitalization program will develop, field, and sustain warfighter capabilities to meet evolving threats and mission support requirements through Block or
 discrete modification or modernization programs depending on mission urgency, available funding, and programmatic and technical risks. Post-production requirements


