Marine Corps (USMC) Marine Corps Communications Systems MCPC 112107. As part of the Joint Enterprise Network Manager (JENM) Joint Program budget strategy,
the Air Force and Army budget for approximately one-third each of the total Program funds for JENM efforts. The Navy and USMC combined funding equals the other
one-third of the JENM Program funding. Prior to the year of execution, Navy and Air Force funding is consolidated in the Army PE (0605031A) and software sustainment
